external_knowledge:
- "Unexplored treasures" refers to products the user has not viewed or purchased;
- "Allure" refers to the recommendation score;
- "Discovered" refers to products viewed by the user;
- "Acquired" refers to products purchased by the user.

sql:
SELECT product_id, purchase_price
FROM product_purchases
WHERE payment_method = 'paypal' AND payment_status = 'pending';
